Articles.Content:
Is anyone else noticing that add-on projects managed on GitHub are having trouble with some site functionality?

I'm noticing that I can't preview documents I edit, drag and drop batches of files into a project, display project graphs, or list contributors. I was surprised I could send a support request to them.

Looks like they addressed it after I sent that request.

Edited May 9, 2017 by Gordon Fecyk
GitHub fixed
